辈的少花点钱的概念以我的理解就是能不买的就不买，贵的不买，别的东西可以代替的不用买，吃饭吃饱就行，喝水解渴就行，住的地方能睡觉就行，每天在家吃饱了就别瞎花钱出去买别的吃的，这炸串那雪糕的，在家吃饱得了呗. 另一个把钱拿去投资买这个东西了买那个东西了，结交好友聚会吃饭联络感情，这些钱能不花就不花. 以上只是我个人的一个想法，谁也不想成为没钱的人，我也希望有一大笔的存款，但实在不懂得怎么存钱，借此也向各位懂事长们求教一下!"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8abcc47199f7fdf21cf3b81d7f13a1d2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/667961299"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI+tbK08bq1f5wEAMaCTExMDcxMzgxNyCG5MS3BjAAOJoBQBxyCTY2Nzk2MTI5OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1727187581.151199", "card_id": "Q_666450363", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "上班很累了，还可以去跑步吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "上班已经非常累了，比如加班时间长，压力大，头脑沉重，精疲力尽了，这种情况下还可以跑步吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a7a22e00b09fa9779b20a22cfc90f87_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/666450363"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+tbK08bq1f5wEAMaCTExMDM3ODA2OCCGtu+2BjAAOEhAHXIJNjY2NDUwMzYzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}